<bug>
    <id>84953</id>
    <title>Reducing the image size with handles on top/bottom/left side/right side, will result in proportional resizing</title>
    <description>
        <paragraph id="1">
            <sentence id="1.1">Created attachment 107760
Compressing the image size in Libreoffice writer  from (top/bottom/left side/ right side) will provide a result of reducing the whole size of that image</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="2">
            <sentence id="2.1">Operating System: Windows 8
LibreOffice Writer Version: 4.3.0.2</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="3">
            <sentence id="3.1">When comparing with "Microsoft word" but not worked in "LibreOffice Writer"</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="4">
            <sentence id="4.1">If i trying to compress any image size by placing the cursor at top centered green box and dragging towards bottom, it will reducing its size from all the sides moves towards to bottom centered green box.</sentence>
            <sentence id="4.2">But this will not occurred in Microsoft word.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="5">
            <sentence id="5.1">STEP TO REPRODUCE:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="6">
            <sentence id="6.1">1 Open LibreOffice Writer.</sentence>
            <sentence id="6.2">2 Go to Insert--&gt;Image--&gt;from file</sentence>
            <sentence id="6.3">3 Select any image and press open.</sentence>
            <sentence id="6.4">4 Now place the cursor at the top centered green box and drag towards to the bottom.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="7">
            <sentence id="7.1">Actual Result:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="8">
            <sentence id="8.1">If trying to compressing the image it will reducing its whole size from all sides.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="9">
            <sentence id="9.1">Expected Result:</sentence>
        </paragraph>
        <paragraph id="10">
            <sentence id="10.1">If trying to compressing the image it should compress as it is.</sentence>
        </paragraph>
    </description>
</bug>
